    "result": {"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h1>emotion과 react-component 같이 쓰기</h1>\n<h2>1. npm trends</h2>\n<h3>npm trends를 찾아보면 emotion이 styled-components의 다운로드 수를 앞서고 있는 것을 알 수 있다.</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/39231312c6b821f684858da3fff1284a/a4e81/emotion-npm-trends.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 41.66666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/39231312c6b821f684858da3fff1284a/a59e9/emotion-npm-trends.webp 192w,\n/static/39231312c6b821f684858da3fff1284a/0ca9f/emotion-npm-trends.webp 384w,\n/static/39231312c6b821f684858da3fff1284a/dc9b9/emotion-npm-trends.webp 768w,\n/static/39231312c6b821f684858da3fff1284a/e2c2f/emotion-npm-trends.webp 1152w,\n/static/39231312c6b821f684858da3fff1284a/6e61e/emotion-npm-trends.webp 1322w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/39231312c6b821f684858da3fff1284a/3b721/emotion-npm-trends.png 192w,\n/static/39231312c6b821f684858da3fff1284a/66595/emotion-npm-trends.png 384w,\n/static/39231312c6b821f684858da3fff1284a/fe486/emotion-npm-trends.png 768w,\n/static/39231312c6b821f684858da3fff1284a/d2d74/emotion-npm-trends.png 1152w,\n/static/39231312c6b821f684858da3fff1284a/a4e81/emotion-npm-trends.png 1322w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/39231312c6b821f684858da3fff1284a/fe486/emotion-npm-trends.png\"\n            alt=\"emotion-npm-trends.png\"\n            title=\"emotion-npm-trends.png\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>실제로 emotion을 이용해본 결과 styled-components를 사용할 줄 아시는 분들이라면 금방 익히실 수 있을 거라고 생각한다.</h3>\n<hr>\n<h2>2. emotion with react</h2>\n<p>emotion을 react와 같이 사용하기 위해서는 일단 emotion을 node_modules에 설치해야한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">// Node Package Manager 설치\nnpm i @emotion/css\nnpm i @emotion/react\n\n//styled-components와 유사한 방식의 사용을 위해\nnpm i @emotion/styled</code></pre></div>\n<p>설치가 완료되면 사용해야할 컴포넌트에 import 해야한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> css<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> jsx <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@emotion/react\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>같이 사용하는 예제 코드를 공식문서에 있는 글과 같이 사용하자면</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> css<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> jsx <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@emotion/react'</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> divStyle <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> css<span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n  background-color: hotpink;\n  font-size: 24px;\n  border-radius: 4px;\n  padding: 32px;\n  text-align: center;\n  &amp;:hover {\n    color: white;\n  }\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">App</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">css</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>divStyle<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">Hover to change color.</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이런식으로 styled-components와는 다르게 사용할 태그에 props를 주는 방법도 있다.</p>\n<p>실제로 이를 사용하면 태그 이름을 바꾸지 않아도 된다.</p>\n<p>styled방식을 이용하면</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> styled <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@emotion/styled'</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> DivStyle <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> styled<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>div<span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n  background-color: hotpink;\n  font-size: 24px;\n  border-radius: 4px;\n  padding: 32px;\n  text-align: center;\n  &amp;:hover {\n    color: white;\n  }\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">App</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">DivStyle</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">Hover to change color.</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">DivStyle</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>styled-components에서 많이 사용하던 코드니 익숙하실 거라고 본다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>3. <em>jsx props로 주는 state를 css에서 이용</em></h2>\n<p>emotion, styled-components 전부 이용가능</p>\n<p>포스팅하고 싶었던 핵심은 이것인데</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>openedMenu<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setOpenedMenu<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> onCLickMenu <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useCallback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">setOpenedMenu</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">prev</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token operator\">!</span>prev<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>메뉴창을 열리게 하는 state가 있다.</p>\n<p>아래 콜백함수는 메뉴가 열려있으면 메뉴 버튼을 눌렀을 때 닫고  닫혀있으면 메뉴 버튼을 눌렀을 때 여는 코드이다.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/efd400dacdaf0c0bb9960d526a3baf39/together.gif\" alt=\"together.gif\"></p>\n<p>이것을 구현하기 위해서</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> List <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> styled<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ul<span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: center;\n  margin-left: 40px;\n  @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {\n    flex-direction: column;\n    width: 100%;\n    margin-left: 0;\n    align-items: center;\n//반응형 컴포넌트를 위한 코드\n    display: </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> openedMenu <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>openedMenu <span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"none\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"flex\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">;\n  } ;\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이런 식으로 styled를 짜고</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">List</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">openedMenu</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>openedMenu<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n        </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Item</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n          </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Link</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>/profile<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n            </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">MenuContent</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">프로필</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">MenuContent</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n          </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Link</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n        </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Item</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n        </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Item</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n          </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Link</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>/<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n            </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">MenuContent</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">커뮤니티</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">MenuContent</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n          </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Link</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n        </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Item</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n        </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Item</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n          </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Link</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>/signup<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n            </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">MenuContent</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">회원가입</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">MenuContent</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n          </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Link</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n        </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Item</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n      </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">List</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이렇게 props에 넣어준다면 가능하다 포인트는 prop name과  prop을 사용하여</p>\n<p>name은 styled-component에게 prop은 state를 다룰 수 있게끔 하여 컨트롤 하는 것이다.</p>\n<p>이러한 방식은 emotion/styled가 아닌 styled-components에서도 사용할 수 있고 인터랙티브 한 웹을 제작하기 위해 알아두면 좋은 방식이다.</p>\n<h3>첫 글은 emotion 사용,  emotion에서 styled 이용, styled-components를 사용할 때 jsx props와 연결하는 방법을 포스팅하였다.</h3>\n<h3>다음 포스팅은 react에서 많이 사용되는 useMemo와 useCallback에 대한 내용을 최대한 이해가 와닿게끔 포스팅해보겠다.</h3>","frontmatter":{"title":"리액트에 이모션 적용하기","summary":"emotion-styled와 react-component의 props를 이어보자.","date":"2021.10.13.","categories":["React","Design"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/dcb1b92c98fcfc68602381dd13834861/175be/react.jpg","srcSet":"/static/dcb1b92c98fcfc68602381dd13834861/5905a/react.jpg 240w,\n/static/dcb1b92c98fcfc68602381dd13834861/b19bf/react.jpg 480w,\n/static/dcb1b92c98fcfc68602381dd13834861/175be/react.jpg 960w","sizes":"(min-width: 960px) 960px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/dcb1b92c98fcfc68602381dd13834861/4a319/react.webp 240w,\n/static/dcb1b92c98fcfc68602381dd13834861/0df1a/react.webp 480w,\n/static/dcb1b92c98fcfc68602381dd13834861/eeb31/react.webp 960w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 960px) 960px, 100vw"}]},"width":960,"height":540}},"publicURL":"/static/dcb1b92c98fcfc68602381dd13834861/react.jpg"}}}}]}},"page